<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4401270>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Maximum credibility tree from Bayesian phylogenetic analysis of the mitochondrial DNA COI gene of all 42 Abantiades sequences used and the ♀ specimens for A. macropusinsulariae and A. pallida. Posterior probabilities greater than 0.7 are shown at each node. Details for all sequences including GenBank accessions are available in Table S1." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4401270/files/figure.png" .

